{"tid":1807994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教車師傅失控剷上行人路 一男子昏迷","createTime":"2020-01-02T06:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T12:20:54.000Z","uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc8e7c8ff7515f667216ba205a366f26b7cb22d","tid":1807994,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"中午約12時，一名教車師傅駕駛客貨車，沿油塘茶果嶺道西行，突失控穿過工程水馬，越過對面線，鏟上油塘站對開行人路撞牆，其間撞倒兩名分別過路及等過路男途人，1人半昏迷，另1人清醒，現場留下大灘血迹。兩人稍後由救護車送聯合醫院救治。警員接報到場調查，司機報稱疑機件故障，不能剎車。他被帶上警車問話。警方正調查意外原因。"},{"pid":"96a60e387688ce66941def7e047385892cfbb474","tid":1807994,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:01:50.000Z","msg":"油塘果個位好垃圾<br />\n好難揸"},{"pid":"37632bd70da872c813e6bb938074a52f8a7bb9f5","tid":1807994,"uid":334861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:01:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2b6d46da637b0d98ac5305368ae35a1853a55ce","tid":1807994,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGPisQq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGPisQq.png&h=47451078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWXjWJM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWXjWJM.png&h=ff6798e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdNv3oM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdNv3oM.png&h=0d24c6bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"298540d6b8db33454aa2897a18b2e87d47aaecae","tid":1807994,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b6d46da637b0d98ac5305368ae35a1853a55ce","tid":1807994,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGPisQq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGPisQq.png&h=47451078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWXjWJM.png\" dat